CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, National edition, October 15, 1938, pg. 21, reads: "Actress Visits Pittsburgh - Mrs. Frances Williams, an actress in stage production, 'You Can't Take It With You,' shown at the Nixon theatre in Pittsburgh last week. Sitting with Mrs. Williams is Detective John Brown of New York.  They were guests at the Loendi Club."
TitMainTitle: Actor Frances Williams and Detective John Brown seated in Loendi Club, another version
